column5: Wow, spectacular PB limey   Congratz    She's gorgeous!!!
Awsome walleye Simon - nicely done! - and great video.   Tracker (Don)
That's a fatso
Awesome fish!!  Congrats.  Must have felt good slipping her back down the hole.  Warm and fuzzies kinda good.  cheers
Man Simon your just killin me with these videos. My son and I watched the Laker one while we ate lunch at my desk. How awesome

Guhhh....that's a TANK!!! Amazing man....way to go on that   Now.  You *think* you do better when you're alone.....just wait pal.  The day is coming when I call you and say I'm on my way...look out!!!

Thanks to the whole gang for the encouraging replies.....it came at the right time to restore my confidence...i was almost on a hatrick of skunkpoos for walleye.    I dont actually eat that much believe it or not,i have lots of happy, well fed friends and neighbours    Its possible just improbable....lol...how's it goin Rick...another year goin bye without hookin up?    Wow....what a truly Phalic reply...   Git 'er done JB...i'm waiting for the call

[quote name='limeyangler' date='12 January 2011 - 02:39 PM'  Wow....what a truly Phalic reply...    My roomies found a box of kleenex and a fish calendar on my bed once...  They've never let me live it down!!
Congrats on your PB Simon   Beauty hawg Are you sure you weren't fishing on Lac Seul?? Leechman
Very nice fish Limey!!!

I'm sure Jacques...but this lake is only a few minutes up the road and is like having Lac Seul on the doorstep (for walleye anyway), I really need a 4 wheeler so i can get in there in the summer!    Thanks Bernie
Solid fish Simon, very nice.  I won't hate on you this time since it's your PB ice eye.
LOL.Spiel...thanks...mind you i usually take the hating as i sign i'm doing something right!
Exactly! Or you could view as I must be doing something wrong.

Hi all,  Went out for a couple of hours at 3pm. Was not expecting to catch anything....as i'd skunked for walleye the last 2 times i'bve been to this lake in the last 2 weeks. I was however under orders to get supper......pressure was on!  The pressure increased because i managed to get a decent eater (16") on the ice almost immediately...then NADA for about half an hour until the BEAST hit, holy man was she a big girl....28" long and probably the same around...belly on it was huge....MY NEW ICEFISHING WALLEYE PB!!!! well pleased with that. The reason the pressure had increased though is i could not bring myself to keep her...back she went and i still needed another fish(at least ) for supper purposes.  Well i got another about 16" and supper was delicious tonight, great little session again...and got the walleye skunk off my back in style.  I always seem to do sooooo much better when i fish alone....weird...but true.
